Package hw1.type.output

This package consists of basic input data types.
As has been described, AnswerScore and Evluator are listed here.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerScore
    Answer Score contains an answer as an object.
    It should be regarded as a component rather a supertype.
    AnswerScore_Type
    Answer Score contains an answer.
    Evaluator
    This is the format output for all three scoring methods.
    Annotators may use this type to give a full output in a unified format way and contain enough information.
